{"tid":536866,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"方丈講場　澳門統計局　15年普通話人口增3倍　中國官商 現已 狂送仔女 做澳門政府要職","createTime":"2018-01-22T07:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T08:26:53.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"85e76766e3b7dbbef832732bdfa04f96d0c9972b","tid":536866,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau/photos/a.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558/584145971928612/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fabbotmacau%2Fphotos%2Fa.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558%2F584145971928612%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=24875973\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau/photos/a.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558/584145971928612/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\nLola Mac:<br />\n題外話，方丈點睇狂補送學生返大陸讀書單野呀？<br />\n<br />\n澳門方丈聯盟:<br />\n咪送囉<br />\n大陸就狂送大陸商官仔女來做政府要職<br />\n仲記唔記得&quot;特殊渠道&quot;新聞?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mcnews.cc/p/17265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmcnews.cc%2Fp%2F17265&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=f0a432b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://mcnews.cc/p/17265</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mcnews.cc/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/153478958054547_1358969134172184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmcnews.cc%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F153478958054547_1358969134172184.jpg&h=7102a763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「特殊渠道」事件由理工內地生李同學「自爆」後，澳門理工學院、公職局、社文司和行政法務司先後否認「政府部門特殊渠道招聘」的機制，但多日以來的報道揭發，政府當局長年在翻譯人員並非不足的情況下，多次以「個人勞動合同」方式，跳過正常開考招聘渠道聘用翻譯人員，當中不乏來自中國的非本澳居民；同時理工有個別講師，只推薦日間中葡翻譯課程的內地生，直接透過「特殊渠道」進入政府部門的招聘面試。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在這樣「差別待遇」的情況下，理工院長李向玉今日（26日）卻稱，內地畢業生進入澳門政府工作「不算少」，而校方亦不需要任何特殊機制將學生送入公職，指學生自行會尋找工作，更稱「澳門更要以廣闊的胸懷擁抱世界，坐上祖國發展的時代列車。」<br />\n<br />\n而理工今日亦回覆《愛瞞》查詢時再澄清，理工是向來依法治校，按章辦事。對於理工語言暨翻譯學校一名吳姓女講師，向多名內地生推薦至政府部門入職面試，理工指其私人行為並不知悉，但在一般情況下，教師為學生升學或就業提供推薦信之類行為，乃國際慣常做法，並不違反大學教師之職業操守，也不違反理工人事章程。理工還表示，於院外兼職申報有既定程序，如有相關證據，著以舉報交由院方依法處理。<br />\n<br />\n而《愛瞞》就事件向理工學院語言暨翻譯學校的吳姓女講師查詢，至今仍未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：<br />\n<br />\n「特殊渠道」＝個人勞動合同外聘？<br />\n<br />\n陳海帆稱無資料顯示李同學已被部門聘用<br />\n<br />\n消息指事發後聘用已取消<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/8mswF3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F8mswF3&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=afcd2472\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/8mswF3</a><br />\n<br />\n有隱瞞？<br />\n<br />\n譚司：理工告知「特殊渠道」並不存在<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/xL94S2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FxL94S2&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=6b9753de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/xL94S2</a><br />\n<br />\n「特殊渠道」事件<br />\n<br />\n消息指一理工講師推薦多名內地生<br />\n<br />\n政府本地翻譯員受「走後門」影響打擊士氣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/ti5bNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fti5bNw&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=0fdd32f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ti5bNw</a><br />\n<br />\n理工畢業生稱「特殊渠道招聘入政府工」引起熱議<br />\n<br />\n理工聲明：校方沒有相關推薦機制<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/B2DPmG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FB2DPmG&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=bd337c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/B2DPmG</a><br />\n<br />\n（澳門日報）李同學：已獲政府部門聘用<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Bi9VWR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FBi9VWR&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=653be639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Bi9VWR</a><br />\n<br />\n相關文章：<br />\n<br />\n「特殊渠道」𠝹開了公務員公平入職的裂痕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Z5u9vD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZ5u9vD&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=86006649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Z5u9vD</a><br />\n<br />\n從澳門公職法律及人事行政制度<br />\n<br />\n分析「內地生『特殊渠道』入職政府工月袋四萬」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/GVnQpn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FGVnQpn&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=71d14e07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/GVnQpn</a><br />\n<br />\n投訴理工學院教師涉嫌違法協助內地生在本澳尋找工作<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Ggsj5L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FGgsj5L&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=a1af2e46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Ggsj5L</a>"},{"pid":"cbc4942ceb84139c37187f3dfd99e876623e2c01","tid":536866,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奶共下場"},{"pid":"23ef5fd1fc37df4d33680c0352cd55a771c656e5","tid":536866,"uid":61675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:01:31.000Z","msg":"最慘係唔奶共果班"},{"pid":"00573f6a6107822bca21d778eb40ca18375aa7fd","tid":536866,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:10:07.000Z","msg":"珠海市澳門區 珠海市海島區"},{"pid":"d98dd2082efc265d4beeed83a63f4c8fc672530c","tid":536866,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:11:08.000Z","msg":"澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8648ea2a8b0e88da222f9f576581594b834e4158","tid":536866,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau/photos/a.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558/584145971928612/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fabbotmacau%2Fphotos%2Fa.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558%2F584145971928612%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=988276c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau/photos/a.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558/584145971928612/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIvan Kuan:<br />\n老一輩黎黎去去都係戈套論調<br />\n「學多種唔代表會被取締」<br />\n「中國都想保育粵語」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAnji Cheong:<br />\n如果有日立法講粵語係犯法就開心了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李燦域:<br />\n其實到依家仲有大把人將「書面語」同匪語混淆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n卓立:<br />\n港澳不斷沉淪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLok Ka Fong:<br />\n以前講普通話的人都會學廣東話，而家調轉要你本地人學普通話適應佢。特別係官台幾日前某學校老師的訪問，完全證明黎種情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKevin Ho:<br />\n<br />\n營造一個對普通話有利嘅社會。<br />\n<br />\n到北佬嚮職場上玩晒嘅時候，啲人先發覺&quot;金翅仆街鳥&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMarjorie Joby:<br />\n<br />\n我仔學校都要佢返屋企同我地家長講普通話，我話唔可以，邊個係屋企講普通話我罰邊個. 屋企個個講廣東話."},{"pid":"e753db104516ca65133d91fbfc53900a71e4c602","tid":536866,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:26:53.000Z","msg":"&quot;有關係就什麼都沒關係&quot;<br />\n何特首普通話溜不溜?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}